data.description: FINALLY! A house for sale in Lake Haven! 4 bedrooms 2.5 bathroom! 2 wood burning fireplaces! Sitting on over 1.5 acres! There is so much land! 2 car attached garage in addition to the 4 car oversized detached garage! A collector's or mechanic's dream garage! Lovely home with 3 bedrooms upstairs and one in the finished basement. House needs some cosmetic updates but has great bones. You won't find this type of land and garage space anywhere else.    There is a $700 annual assessment
